# mcp-note-ingest

Day 21 MCP server skeleton for the Local-First Markdown Vault App project.

## What this does today

This is only the server skeleton.

It currently supports:

- stdio transport
- `initialize`
- `tools/list`
- one smoke-test tool: `ping`

## What comes next

On Day 22, this server will gain the real tool:

- `ingest_chat_markdown`

That tool will write Markdown files into the vault.

## Run the server

```bash
cd tools/mcp-note-ingest
npm start